      "content": "Task brief at .synapse/tasks/27.md\n\n# Rename: activities → tasks\n\nThe \"Activities\" concept is being renamed to \"Tasks\" throughout the codebase. This is a UI label + internal naming change. The MCP tool names (`start_activity`, `finish_activity`, `delegate_task`, `report_done`) are part of the agent API used by live agents — **do NOT rename those tool names**. Everything else should be renamed.\n…",
